track_notes: Starting from Italia you can park on the side of the road; wonderfull landscape, big cross on summit.

Easy track if you go up and down from Castello. 
I made a 2 days round trip. The ridge between Tre Chiosis and Pt Joanne is quite difficult ( classif EE ) follow this way ONLY if you are EXPERT and have HELMET for safety.
track_title: class E by normal way , NO Phone, NO good x VHF
